{"tid":1047352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共增干預　港恐失世貿成員身份","createTime":"2019-03-05T01:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T11:13:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"54ac08fad06c004317858e898b619a94e0a9a85f","tid":1047352,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190305/large/05la3p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190305%2Flarge%2F05la3p12.jpg&h=bee6b98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獨立關稅區的原意是世界貿易組織（WTO）希望為未獲得獨立的殖民地政府而設置，令它們有經濟上自主權。一國兩制下香港只有外交及國防事務由中國直接管理，香港可以中國香港名義參與國際組織，在經貿層面可與其他國家商討合作。<br />\n<br />\n香港是世界貿易組織一個非主權國成員，國際社會普遍承認香港在經濟上的獨立地位。不過，世貿規定成員需要在對外貿易關係和參與WTO事務上享有「完全的自治權」，不得受到所屬國家的干涉才能夠保持成員身份，意味一旦中國政府在經貿層面施以干預，世貿有權取消香港的成員身份。<br />\n<br />\n企業棄港上市　金融服務瓜得<br />\n<br />\n若美國撤銷香港獨立關稅地位，最直接影響的就是香港出口美國貨品會被徵重稅，進出口貿易行業首當其衝。一旦美國對港政策轉變會引起連鎖效應，恐影響香港金融和國際商貿中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學者關焯照指，「若香港變成另一個中國城市，外界對你信心會減低好多，香港金融城市地位一定會受到好大衝擊」。他預期若出現最壞情況，外國企業不會再在香港設立地區總部，企業不會到港上市。自由黨黨魁、立法會紡織及製衣界議員鍾國斌認為，一旦美國取消香港獨立關稅地位，甚至改變《香港政策法》，香港金融服務和專業服務這兩條支柱都「瓜得」，美國更可能限制高科技輸入香港。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃尹華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626483&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=4799ea23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626483&h=325711a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626483</a>"},{"pid":"1267653eb3e7ae812ec4284b61dc11731c87f176","tid":1047352,"uid":155095,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"一國一制，融入大灣區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9369675ee0eece4605313eb7d1da7387bb6eec39","tid":1047352,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1267653eb3e7ae812ec4284b61dc11731c87f176","tid":1047352,"uid":155095,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"一國一制，融入大灣區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"成為大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902056e589e81e5fab676ccb81ccd71fb18e5605","tid":1047352,"uid":18477,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他預期若出現最壞情況，外國企業不會再在香港設立地區總部，企業不會到港上市。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n現在進行式啦仲預期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af959c2ccb9e5836ad9ee7549aea17938d7d5e7","tid":1047352,"uid":34466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"寧為玉碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345969ed9f4da369f8c7c0c58371eda883f1ff4e","tid":1047352,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"有大灣區同祖國支持，驚閪咩 ！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7eada8deece1863e1c831dc0ebd6cf381b3e80","tid":1047352,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"我最期待.jpg"},{"pid":"19216a058cfabfcbcb0b75def0a39659ca559671","tid":1047352,"uid":43983,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"最好快撚D，港哩唔使再炒樓，大陸人唔使走資/走佬黎香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我迫不及待要好好玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse