"hkgmoji\" /> 老實講而家除左坐等舉國淪喪 都無乜野做到<br />\n五十年不變 廿五年都未夠已經變曬 <br />\n快點來強姦我！"},{"pid":"0a12e7912c9259ecf9335abd75045490906a5e7d","tid":1047352,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f1218d96e143c9cf3d3843d6c04b04ccd3272ee0","tid":1047352,"uid":179409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"902056e589e81e5fab676ccb81ccd71fb18e5605","tid":1047352,"uid":18477,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他預期若出現最壞情況，外國企業不會再在香港設立地區總部，企業不會到港上市。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n現在進行式啦仲預期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"近幾年都轉晒去新加坡啦<br />\n篇文係咪幾年前架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp360.jsp?tableID=133&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp360.jsp%3FtableID%3D133%26ID%3D0%26productType%3D8&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=09a62ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp360.jsp?tableID=133&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8</a><br />\n鳩噏唔洗本<br />\n其實連登仔真係要認識下香港<br />\n香港個根基厚到俾支那搞咗廿年仲要冇晒法治自由都仲好有地位，真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"02718c380271368a1ba9d98a357993941f162130","tid":1047352,"uid":83609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"快啦唔好得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080d755899c57ccae2bac080f28b717ff0d9c897","tid":1047352,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"支持，大家都係中國人<br />\n稅區應該都要一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1911a6c2e7d03b629cc6d7ef33a17f396192fb","tid":1047352,"uid":34553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca1cce2